snippet.title: Osmos Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.hemispheregames.com/osmos

Enter the Darwinian world of a galactic mote -- absorb or be absorbed. Winner of multiple "Game of the Year" awards, Osmos features unique physics-based play, stellar graphics, and a hypnotic soundtrack of ambient electronica. Available on iOS, Android, PC, Mac and Linux.

Music by Gas / High Skies. http://microscopics.co.uk
Video editing by Kun Chang. http://www.kunchang.net
